WEBVTT

00:00.007 --> 00:02.987
FLOOR

00:05.577 --> 00:06.477
<b>Uh-oh.{ep05@22:09}</b>

00:07.707 --> 00:12.997
<b>Arai, you just... went <i>down</i> the stairs, right?{ep05@22:13}</b>

00:13.577 --> 00:14.347
<b>What?{ep05@22:18}</b>

00:18.257 --> 00:21.887
F{*\c&H365A7E&}LO{*\c&H416E93&}OR

00:18.767 --> 00:21.297
<b>Kobeni! Make peace signs and stand still.</b>

00:21.297 --> 00:21.887
<b>{Weh}Uh...</b>

00:28.847 --> 00:30.017
<b>Oh, my.</b>

00:35.397 --> 00:38.147
<b>Aki, what do you make of this?</b>

00:38.527 --> 00:40.947
<b>Must be a devil's ability.</b>

00:42.327 --> 00:44.167
<b>Kobeni, stand there.</b>

00:54.847 --> 00:55.697
<b>Huh?</b>

00:57.047 --> 00:59.457
<b>Why is there a room
 on the other side of the windows?</b>

01:18.117 --> 01:20.617
<b>Hey! We can't get out through any of the windows!</b>

01:20.617 --> 01:22.457
<b>They just loop back to the other side!</b>

01:23.487 --> 01:25.067
<b>Just as I feared, then.</b>

01:26.257 --> 01:29.927
<b>We can't leave the eighth floor.</b>

01:27.447 --> 01:28.077
FLOOR

01:40.337 --> 01:41.997
<b>Let's look at our situation.</b>

01:42.407 --> 01:48.627
<b>Likely due to a devil's ability, whether we go up or down the stairs, we end up on the eighth floor again.</b>

01:48.987 --> 01:51.007
<b>For some reason, we can't use the elevator.</b>

01:49.757 --> 01:51.007
FIRE
EXTINGUISHER

