01:51.507 --> 01:54.017
<b>We can't get out via the windows in the rooms.</b>

01:54.557 --> 01:57.827
<b>Going through the ceiling
 also leads back to the eighth floor.</b>

01:59.417 --> 02:03.397
<b>It's probably because
 Power killed that devil just now.</b>

02:03.817 --> 02:06.597
<b>It died with its ability to lock people in activated.</b>

02:06.597 --> 02:07.487
<b>That devil was—</b>

02:07.487 --> 02:09.097
<b>You said to kill it!</b>

02:09.097 --> 02:09.777
<b>Did not!</b>

02:09.777 --> 02:14.037
<b>When a devil dies, its abilities
 are deactivated, so it can't be that.</b>

02:14.347 --> 02:16.787
<b>Aki, how is the flesh piece reacting?</b>

02:17.217 --> 02:18.287
<b>Well...</b>

02:18.747 --> 02:21.377
<b>It's stopped reacting entirely.</b>

02:21.787 --> 02:26.187
<b>So it used that small devil to lure us into a trap.</b>

02:26.187 --> 02:29.507
<b>I've never seen a devil act in such a roundabout way.</b>

02:29.507 --> 02:32.757
<b>But if we stay trapped in here for long enough,</b>

02:32.757 --> 02:35.897
<b>other devil hunters will come to our aid...</b>

02:37.647 --> 02:42.267
<b>And we'll need to pray
 that they don't get trapped just like us.</b>

02:44.117 --> 02:47.277
<b>We're all going to die here.</b>

02:47.757 --> 02:50.277
<b>We're going to starve to death.</b>

02:50.277 --> 02:52.757
<b>Kobeni! Get a grip!</b>

02:52.757 --> 02:56.447
<b>Remember how you want to make money
 to send your brother to university!</b>

02:56.447 --> 02:58.657
<b>That was basically forced on me.</b>

02:59.007 --> 03:05.167
<b>My brother is very smart, so my parents
 had me work to get money for his education.</b>

03:05.847 --> 03:10.797
<b>It was either prostitution or devil hunting.</b>

03:13.297 --> 03:17.017
<b>I wanted to go to university too!</b>

03:17.017 --> 03:21.617
<b>B-But I'm going to die in this place!</b>

03:26.527 --> 03:28.027
<b>That face!</b>

03:29.567 --> 03:31.317
<b>You piece of shit!</b>

03:31.667 --> 03:33.117
<b>Stop laughing!</b>

03:33.757 --> 03:38.497
<b>Kobeni, devils love fear.</b>

03:38.497 --> 03:41.577
<b>If you get scared,
 you're giving them what they want.</b>

03:41.887 --> 03:45.007
<b>But I <i>am</i> scared!</b>

03:46.037 --> 03:47.837
<b>Thinking about something, Aki?</b>

03:51.077 --> 03:52.467
<b>The clock.</b>

03:52.977 --> 03:55.717
<b>It's been stuck at 8:18 this whole time.</b>

03:55.717 --> 04:00.217
<b>The clocks in all the rooms
 are stuck at the same time.</b>

04:02.617 --> 04:08.267
<b>It's possible that a devil's ability
 has stopped time on this floor.</b>

04:08.267 --> 04:11.307
<b>If that's the case, no help is likely to come.{talk about driving the team morale down into the ground, lol}</b>

04:14.167 --> 04:15.307
<b>Awesome!</b>

04:15.307 --> 04:16.987
<b>We can sleep all we want!</b>

04:18.597 --> 04:20.367
<b>How stupid are you?!</b>

04:20.727 --> 04:25.247
<b>We might be stuck in here forever!</b>

04:25.247 --> 04:28.847
<b>We might, or we might not.</b>

04:28.847 --> 04:30.127
<b>Wake me up when you find out.</b>

04:30.427 --> 04:32.447
<b>Look at this nice bed.</b>

04:32.447 --> 04:33.877
<b>It's a waste not to sleep in it.</b>

04:34.387 --> 04:37.137
<b>Thanks for the free nap, mister devil.</b>

04:47.377 --> 04:48.487
<b>He's out...</b>

04:52.927 --> 04:54.147
<b>Denji!</b>

04:54.447 --> 04:56.787
<b>Denji, wake up already.</b>

05:03.737 --> 05:06.627
<b>What, did we escape already?</b>

05:06.627 --> 05:08.667
<b>Unfortunately, not yet.</b>

05:09.237 --> 05:13.677
<b>We did find out that we have running water and electricity.{somewhat of a nitpick, can skip: there should be a "while you were sleeping" somewhere in this sentence, but I guess it's already implied/obvious.}</b>

05:13.677 --> 05:18.677
<b>And we found some food that the guests
 left behind when they fled the hotel.</b>

05:19.007 --> 05:22.677
<b>But really, we're all close to our wits' ends.</b>

05:23.357 --> 05:26.187
<b>Aki keeps looking for the devil.</b>

05:26.717 --> 05:30.057
<b>I told him to rest a bit, but he won't listen.</b>

05:30.497 --> 05:34.087
<b>Arai was helping Aki at the start,</b>

05:34.087 --> 05:37.567
<b>but now he's succumbed to fear
 and is holed up in one of the rooms.</b>

05:38.007 --> 05:42.577
<b>Kobeni went a little crazy and tried to drink
 water from a toilet, so I knocked her out.</b>

05:43.027 --> 05:45.197
<b>As for the fiend girl...</b>

05:45.797 --> 05:47.457
<b>What's Power doing?</b>

05:47.457 --> 05:50.707
<b>I was bored, so I came up with a Nobel prize.</b>

05:50.707 --> 05:55.457
<b>If I invent a new Nobel prize, humans are going to prostrate themselves before me.</b>

05:55.457 --> 06:00.187
<b>And then I'll use that situation to become the prime minister!</b>

06:00.187 --> 06:03.467
<b>After all, I wish to see humans suffering.</b>

06:03.967 --> 06:07.227
<b>I'll start by raising the sales tax rate to 100%!</b>

06:08.657 --> 06:09.957
<b>She seems normal to me.</b>

06:09.957 --> 06:10.477
<b>Ah.</b>

06:11.157 --> 06:12.347
<b>Alrighty, then.</b>

06:13.397 --> 06:16.227
<b>Let's all keep an eye on Kobeni and Arai.</b>

06:34.407 --> 06:37.127
<b>Well, here goes my last cigarette.</b>

06:37.487 --> 06:39.627
<b>It's boring how calm you are.</b>

06:40.007 --> 06:44.887
<b>Aki is working hard, so I can take it easy.</b>

06:44.887 --> 06:47.267
<b>There's also the power of nicotine.</b>

06:47.697 --> 06:51.017
<b>It's nice being dependent on something.</b>

06:51.347 --> 06:54.767
<b>Who doesn't want something they can depend on in their life?</b>

06:55.127 --> 06:57.277
<b>That cigarette brand seems familiar.</b>

07:00.577 --> 07:05.657
<b>Well, I was the one who introduced Aki
 to the taste of cigarettes.</b>

07:10.447 --> 07:12.167
<b>Want a cig, Aki?</b>

07:12.527 --> 07:14.417
<b>Smoking erodes the bones.</b>

07:14.417 --> 07:17.167
<b>It helps you socialize, though.</b>

07:17.167 --> 07:19.417
<b>I don't intend to get close to anyone.</b>

07:23.487 --> 07:26.117
<b>Let me guess why you've come to the Bureau.</b>

07:26.117 --> 07:28.177
<b>To kill the Gun Devil, right?</b>

07:29.927 --> 07:33.447
<b>Every gloomy person in here came for that reason.</b>

07:33.967 --> 07:37.817
<b>This is the only place allowed to have pieces of it.</b>

07:38.377 --> 07:42.067
<b>As a devil hunter, you're not likely
 to live too long, so might as well smoke.</b>

07:42.877 --> 07:44.817
<b>I won't die that easily.</b>

07:45.327 --> 07:46.697
<b>Yeah, please don't.</b>

07:47.187 --> 07:49.947
<b>It's a huge hassle to have your partner die.</b>

07:51.367 --> 07:54.207
PHARMACY

07:51.367 --> 07:54.207
PHARMACY

07:54.207 --> 07:57.207


07:57.837 --> 07:59.067
<b>What was that?</b>

08:03.047 --> 08:07.197
<b>It's common to get trouble
 from a dead partner's loved ones.</b>

08:07.197 --> 08:10.977
<b>She doesn't have the power to kill{tlc, more towards a suggestion: take revenge on?}{too long} the devil,
 so she takes it out on me.{timing: until: watashi ni ataru no}</b>

08:11.527 --> 08:16.677
<b>Well, I tend to just think of it
 as part of a devil hunter's job.</b>

08:25.717 --> 08:27.197
<b>What did you do?</b>

08:30.977 --> 08:34.707
<b>I secretly stuck some gum to her clothes.{lol}</b>

08:36.707 --> 08:37.787
<b>What?!</b>

08:38.127 --> 08:40.137
<b>She got what she deserved.</b>

08:40.137 --> 08:43.227
<b>It's not about you. She just annoyed me.</b>

08:43.227 --> 08:44.797
<b>So I got back at her.</b>

08:45.277 --> 08:46.297
<b>Serves her right.</b>

08:46.647 --> 08:50.037
<b>She'll go on with her life without noticing the gum.</b>

08:56.687 --> 08:58.147
<b>Tenten</b>

08:56.687 --> 08:58.147
<b>Chinese</b>

08:56.687 --> 08:58.147
<b>Restaurant</b>

08:56.687 --> 08:58.147
<b>Tenten</b>

08:56.687 --> 08:58.147
<b>Chinese</b>

08:56.687 --> 08:58.147
<b>Restaurant</b>

