08:58.147 --> 09:00.647
<b>Well, you know, my teacher once told me this.</b>

08:58.147 --> 09:01.147


08:58.147 --> 09:01.147


09:00.967 --> 09:06.427
<b>It's not the strongest or bravest hunters
 that the devils fear most.</b>

09:06.427 --> 09:09.157
<b>It's the crazy ones.</b>

09:09.557 --> 09:12.257
<b>So I think you'll survive for longer.</b>

09:14.157 --> 09:15.577
<b>Is that sarcasm?</b>

09:15.577 --> 09:18.187
<b>I'll take your dessert if you're not eating it.{https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Annin_tofu we could just dumb it down to "jello/jelly"}</b>

09:21.167 --> 09:22.917
<b>You can have this.</b>

09:24.247 --> 09:26.227
<b>They erode the bones.</b>

09:26.227 --> 09:27.427
<b>Really?</b>

09:27.737 --> 09:31.887
<b>Looks like we're going to be together
 for quite a while, so it'd be nice if you smoked too.</b>

09:41.447 --> 09:43.277
<b>Fine, I'll smoke <i>one</i>.</b>

09:43.277 --> 09:46.567
<b>And this will be the only one I smoke with you.{so that was a fucking lie}</b>

09:48.797 --> 09:51.277
<b>Himeno, do you have any smokes left?</b>

09:51.627 --> 09:54.287
<b>Sorry. This is the last one.</b>

09:54.647 --> 09:56.827
<b>Then let me have it.</b>

09:56.827 --> 09:57.917
<b>Really?</b>

09:58.607 --> 10:00.587
<b>Okay, I guess.</b>

10:02.417 --> 10:03.327
<b>That's a kiss!</b>

10:03.327 --> 10:04.007
<b>No fair!</b>

10:04.007 --> 10:05.167
<b>An indirect kiss!</b>

10:05.477 --> 10:06.617
<b>Shut up.</b>

10:10.167 --> 10:11.757
<b>I have bad news.</b>

10:12.797 --> 10:14.807
<b>We killed a devil, right?</b>

10:14.807 --> 10:16.927
<b>The one I killed!</b>

10:17.357 --> 10:20.177
<b>It's growing bigger.</b>

10:31.757 --> 10:34.157
<b>I'm sure I killed it.</b>

10:34.527 --> 10:36.507
<b>It can't get out of the hotel.</b>

10:36.507 --> 10:38.157
<b>I've never seen such a shape.</b>

10:38.727 --> 10:40.487
<b>What devil is this?</b>

10:41.427 --> 10:42.537
<b>Humans!</b>

10:42.537 --> 10:44.357
<b>Hear me, humans.</b>

10:44.357 --> 10:46.297
<b>Hear me, foolish humans.</b>

10:46.297 --> 10:48.797
<b>I wish to negotiate a contract.</b>

10:49.117 --> 10:50.417
<b>It talks!</b>

10:50.417 --> 10:51.427
<b>A contract?</b>

10:51.827 --> 10:55.377
<b>Let me eat the human you call Denji.</b>

10:55.377 --> 10:57.207
<b>I don't mind if he's dead.</b>

10:57.207 --> 10:58.677
<b>Let me eat him.</b>

10:58.677 --> 11:03.307
<b>If you do, I shall let all the other
 devil hunters exit unharmed.</b>

11:03.307 --> 11:05.067
<b>Exit unharmed.</b>

11:05.067 --> 11:06.817
<b>Make the contract!</b>

11:07.167 --> 11:08.247
<b>{I think small voices repeat the}Make the contract!</b>

11:08.247 --> 11:08.817
<b>{I think small voices repeat the}Make the contract!</b>

11:19.217 --> 11:20.407
<b>Denji.</b>

11:20.407 --> 11:21.787
<b>Get eaten.</b>

11:48.767 --> 11:50.317
<b>Keep it down, will ya?</b>

11:50.317 --> 11:53.657
<b>Aki, can't you just have the Fox swallow it and get this over with?</b>

11:54.447 --> 11:55.127
<b>Yip.</b>

11:57.537 --> 11:59.807
<b>Seems like the Fox can't get here,</b>

11:59.807 --> 12:02.147
<b>because this space is isolated from the outside.</b>

12:02.147 --> 12:05.127
<b>Yeah, its body is all the way in Kyoto.</b>

12:05.447 --> 12:08.227
<b>Guess I'll use my Ghost then.</b>

12:20.967 --> 12:21.977
<b>Ugh!</b>

12:21.977 --> 12:23.507
<b>It got bigger.</b>

12:24.717 --> 12:25.977
<b>It's no use.</b>

12:25.977 --> 12:29.227
<b>This is not my actual body.</b>

12:29.227 --> 12:31.987
<b>My heart isn't here.</b>

12:32.307 --> 12:33.987
<b>This is the inside of my belly.</b>

12:33.987 --> 12:34.067
<b>This is the inside of my belly.</b>

12:34.067 --> 12:34.147
<b>This is the inside of my belly.</b>

12:34.457 --> 12:38.237
<b>My weak point is not on the eighth floor.</b>

12:38.557 --> 12:42.247
<b>The only way to get out alive
 is to make the contract.</b>

12:42.247 --> 12:43.627
<b>Hmph!</b>

12:43.627 --> 12:47.307
<b>It's not like you'll actually let them out after you kill me.</b>

12:47.307 --> 12:48.747
<b>You're wrong.</b>

12:48.747 --> 12:52.227
<b>It's saying "contract", right?</b>

12:52.227 --> 12:56.257
<b>When a devil uses the word "contract",
 that holds great power.{become meguca}</b>

12:56.557 --> 13:01.767
<b>If one side upholds their end,
 the other is also forced to.</b>

13:02.107 --> 13:04.387
<b>If they don't, they die.</b>

13:04.387 --> 13:07.667
<b>So there's no doubt
 it would let us out if we gave you to it.</b>

13:08.277 --> 13:11.527
<b>Himeno, we should kill him.</b>

13:12.087 --> 13:16.027
<b>After that's done and we're out, we can consider our options.</b>

13:16.027 --> 13:18.777
<b>Otherwise we'll all just starve to death in here.</b>

13:19.167 --> 13:23.407
<b>It's even allowed by law for hunters
 to make contracts with devils.</b>

13:23.767 --> 13:26.037
<b>We should make that contract!</b>

13:26.437 --> 13:29.237
<b>The devil wants to kill Denji.</b>

13:29.237 --> 13:32.047
<b>That means Denji's death
 would be to the devil's advantage.</b>

13:32.567 --> 13:34.367
<b>So we can't agree to it.</b>

13:34.367 --> 13:35.917
<b>I'm with Aki, then.</b>

13:36.487 --> 13:37.717
<b>Really?!</b>

13:37.717 --> 13:39.437
<b>I'm for killing him!</b>

13:39.437 --> 13:40.427
<b>For real?</b>

13:40.427 --> 13:45.237
<b>Even if I come up with a Nobel prize,
 I can't announce it unless I get out.</b>

13:45.237 --> 13:46.887
<b>Die for my Nobel!</b>

13:46.887 --> 13:49.827
<b>A fiend cannot form a contract with a devil.</b>

13:49.827 --> 13:53.897
<b>So if you kill Denji, the devil won't be forced to let us out.</b>

13:54.377 --> 13:56.467
<b>In any case, we're not killing him.</b>

13:56.467 --> 13:58.407
<b>We're devil hunters.</b>

13:59.097 --> 14:01.157
<b>We only kill devils.</b>

14:01.157 --> 14:02.107
<b>Tch.{tsk}</b>

14:03.907 --> 14:05.477
<b>I'm bored. Let's sumo wrestle!</b>

14:05.477 --> 14:07.657
<b>I don't wanna play after you said to kill me!</b>

14:14.537 --> 14:15.987
<b>I'm hungry.</b>

14:15.987 --> 14:20.177
<b>Aki, do you actually have a plan for how to get out?</b>

14:20.177 --> 14:24.677
<b>If we trust what it says, that means we can't kill it.</b>

14:24.987 --> 14:27.427
<b>But I don't intend to kill Denji either.</b>

14:27.847 --> 14:30.187
<b>But we're going to starve unless we do something.</b>

14:33.747 --> 14:36.027
<b>If we run out of options, I'll use the sword.</b>

14:36.027 --> 14:37.187
<b>That's not an option.</b>

14:38.827 --> 14:42.807
<b>If using the sword would solve this,
 why don't you do it?</b>

14:43.967 --> 14:46.827
<b>Even if we run out of options,
 we're not using the sword.</b>

14:47.487 --> 14:49.707
<b>If we get to that point, I'm sorry, but...</b>

14:50.077 --> 14:51.707
<b>you'll have to die.</b>

14:52.267 --> 14:53.957
<b>What?</b>

14:53.957 --> 14:55.707
<b>Gone?!</b>

14:55.707 --> 14:57.087
<b>It's gone!</b>

14:57.087 --> 15:00.467
<b>All the food we left on the bed is gone!</b>

15:00.997 --> 15:01.837
<b>How?</b>

15:07.497 --> 15:10.257
<b>Did you eat all of it?!</b>

15:10.257 --> 15:12.727
<b>It wasn't me. It was Denji.</b>

15:12.727 --> 15:14.867
<b>That's an obvious lie!</b>

15:14.867 --> 15:16.227
<b>I get it!</b>

15:16.227 --> 15:19.237
<b>I finally get it!</b>

15:19.977 --> 15:23.957
<b>It's that fiend's ability that's trapping us here!</b>

15:23.957 --> 15:25.617
<b>I'm sure of it!</b>

15:25.617 --> 15:26.617
<b>Nope.</b>

15:26.617 --> 15:28.277
<b>Calm down, Kobeni!</b>

15:28.277 --> 15:29.387
<b>She's the Blood Fiend!</b>

15:29.387 --> 15:31.467
<b>You're taking a fiend's side?</b>

15:31.467 --> 15:33.877
<b>We're supposed to be devil hunters!</b>

15:33.877 --> 15:37.057
<b>Arai, you're on their side!</b>

15:37.057 --> 15:39.007
<b>You were a spy all along!</b>

15:39.007 --> 15:40.257
<b>He's a pie?{it's a pun, the japanese rendering of "spy" sounds close to the word for "sour"}</b>

15:40.257 --> 15:42.677
<b>I-I'm not on their side...</b>

15:43.797 --> 15:46.257
<b>You're definitely a spy!</b>

15:50.977 --> 15:52.087
<b>A scream?</b>

15:52.087 --> 15:53.517
<b>Himeno, run!</b>

16:02.567 --> 16:06.217
<b>Kill Denji and give me his heart!</b>

16:06.217 --> 16:07.967
<b>Give it!</b>

16:07.967 --> 16:10.467
<b>I swell with fear.</b>

16:10.467 --> 16:13.267
<b>I <i>am</i> fear!</b>

16:13.267 --> 16:15.747
<b>Fear more!</b>

16:16.337 --> 16:17.877
<b>Fear death!</b>

16:18.287 --> 16:20.007
<b>Fear everything!</b>

16:20.527 --> 16:24.107
<b>I'm going to kill Chainsaw.</b>

16:24.107 --> 16:25.927
<b>Me!</b>

16:25.927 --> 16:28.807
<b>The Eternity Devil!</b>

16:34.947 --> 16:36.107
<b>The floor slanted!</b>

16:52.387 --> 16:55.727
<b>Give me Denji's heart!</b>

16:55.727 --> 16:56.667
<b>Please!</b>

16:56.667 --> 16:59.167
<b>Someone please kill Denji!</b>

16:59.167 --> 17:00.717
<b>Please do it!</b>

17:00.717 --> 17:02.237
<b>This is getting bad!</b>

17:02.237 --> 17:04.477
<b>Let's feed him to the devil!</b>

17:06.847 --> 17:08.297
<b>I'll use the sword.</b>

17:08.297 --> 17:10.557
<b>You agree, right, Himeno?</b>

17:12.197 --> 17:13.527
<b>Himeno?!</b>

17:14.707 --> 17:15.557
<b>Hey, hey!</b>

17:15.557 --> 17:17.747
<b>What are you doing?</b>

17:17.747 --> 17:21.067
<b>If he uses the sword, we'll be able to get out.</b>

17:21.497 --> 17:25.317
<b>But then the contract would shave off
 a big chunk of Aki's lifespan.</b>

17:25.967 --> 17:29.617
<b>And he still has a lot of things to accomplish.</b>

17:29.617 --> 17:31.987
<b>So, I'm sorry, Denji.</b>

17:32.947 --> 17:34.707
<b>Forgive me!</b>

17:35.037 --> 17:36.707
<b>Hey! Get off me!</b>

17:36.707 --> 17:38.207
<b>Let go!</b>

17:42.457 --> 17:44.457
<b>Die!</b>

18:10.957 --> 18:17.047
<b>I agree that he's a disgusting piece of shit,
 who deserves to be stabbed,</b>

18:17.607 --> 18:20.127
<b>but he strives to kill the Gun Devil.</b>

18:21.147 --> 18:24.717
<b>I can't kill the Gun Devil on my own.</b>

18:25.407 --> 18:33.307
<b>I'd like to have every single
 devil hunter with the guts to face it.</b>

18:34.047 --> 18:36.207
<b>Even if it means I shorten my own life,</b>

18:37.767 --> 18:40.057
<b>I won't let Denji die!</b>

18:41.567 --> 18:42.057
<b>Power!</b>

18:42.487 --> 18:44.067
<b>You're the Blood Fiend, right?</b>

18:44.407 --> 18:46.567
<b>Can you stop his bleeding?</b>

18:46.857 --> 18:50.527
<b>I can only freely command my own blood.</b>

18:50.527 --> 18:52.567
<b>Manipulating another's is difficult.</b>

18:54.577 --> 18:58.827
<b>But if Topknot dies, there will be
 no human to make me meals.</b>

18:59.137 --> 19:01.577
<b>I suppose I can do something.</b>

19:07.867 --> 19:09.217
<b>What do I do?</b>

19:09.637 --> 19:11.217
<b>What do I do?!</b>

19:11.217 --> 19:13.767
<b>Aki! Aki! Aki!</b>

19:13.767 --> 19:14.847
<b>What do I do?!</b>

19:15.237 --> 19:18.107
<b>I-It's not my fault!</b>

19:18.107 --> 19:19.097
<b>It's you!</b>

19:19.097 --> 19:21.107
<b>It's all your fault!</b>

19:21.107 --> 19:25.167
<b>If only you'd just quietly gotten eaten,
 everything would have been fine!</b>

19:26.337 --> 19:27.977
<b>Okay, fine then!</b>

19:27.977 --> 19:30.847
<b>I'll go get eaten then.</b>

19:30.847 --> 19:33.237
<b>I'm so relieved.</b>

19:33.927 --> 19:36.497
<b>But I'm not going quietly.</b>

19:37.417 --> 19:40.997
<b>If I do manage to kill the devil,</b>

19:41.557 --> 19:42.497
<b>then...</b>

19:42.497 --> 19:44.587
<b>I haven't forgotten about that kiss!</b>

19:45.497 --> 19:47.747
<b>Have you any idea of how to kill it?</b>

19:48.257 --> 19:51.757
<b>It hurts a lot, but I'll become Chainsaw.</b>

19:52.157 --> 19:54.057
<b>Ch-Chainsaw?</b>

19:54.057 --> 19:59.187
<b>I'm not sure why, but that devil seems scared of my Chainsaw.</b>

19:59.757 --> 20:04.247
<b>That's why it's telling you all to kill me
 rather than attacking me directly.</b>

20:05.287 --> 20:10.237
<b>Also, when you hit it, it seemed to feel pain.</b>

20:11.007 --> 20:12.607
<b>And that means...</b>

20:12.607 --> 20:15.277
<b>I just need to make the pain so unbearable</b>

20:16.027 --> 20:18.537
<b>that it kills itself!</b>

20:20.067 --> 20:22.037
<b>That how a devil would think!</b>

20:25.367 --> 20:28.037
<b>You protected me.</b>

20:28.467 --> 20:31.167
<b>Mind your own business, shithead.</b>

20:31.817 --> 20:36.167
<b>I'm sick of owing people stuff!</b>

20:36.847 --> 20:39.497
<b>If we get out of this, I'm calling us even!</b>
